public class TupleReducer.Collector
extends TupleReducer.StaticCollector<OUTPUT_KEY,OUTPUT_VALUE,Object,Object>

Base class for collecting data from a TupleReducer in the reduce phase. This non static inner class is created to eliminate the need in of the extended TupleReducer methods to specify the generic types for the Collector meanwhile keeping generics.
